Package Strategy.Algorithms

Class UCT

  • java.lang.Object
    • Strategy.Algorithms.UCT
  • public class UCT
extends java.lang.Object
    Upper Confidence Bound applied to trees.

    The UCT contains one method to compute UCT value.

    The UCT contains one method to find the node with the highest UCT value.

    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Denis Krylov
    See Also:
    Minimax, MonteCarloTreeSearch
